fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "gtktextview-h.html#gtk_text_view_set_border_window_size", "fragment": "Gtk.TextView.SetBorderWindowSize \nSets the width of Gtk.TextWindowType.Left or Gtk.TextWindowType.Right or the height of Gtk.TextWindowType.Top or Gtk.TextWindowType.Bottom. Automatically destroys the corresponding window if the size is set to and creates the window if the size is set to non zero. This function can only be used for the border windows it doesn t work with Gtk.TextWindowType.Widget Gtk.TextWindowType.Text or Gtk.TextWindowType.Private. \nParameters \nwindow to affect \nwidth or height of the window \n"});